




Lightyear Capital






















































Identifying Trends. 
            Discovering Opportunities.
Since 2000, Lightyear Capital has provided private equity capital to a broad spectrum of companies across the financial services industry.  With over $2.5 billion of capital raised, we seek to leverage our sector-focused expertise and market insights to create value in our portfolio for our investors.






Firm

Private Equity Capital for Financial Services

Specialized

            Lightyear is a specialist in financial services, a dynamic and diverse industry representing as much as 20% of the U.S. economy.  Financial services is opportunity rich but oft-overlooked:  regulatory, tax, accounting, and business model complexities all require expertise.  Our knowledge, gained over a decade in financial services, positions Lightyear well to navigate the opportunities of this specialized space.
            

Experienced

            Our Investment Committee has, on average, invested together at Lightyear for 12 years, worked together for over 15 years, and been in financial services for over 30 years, including in senior operational roles.  Having completed over 35 investments since 2000 through its affiliated investment funds, the Lightyear team has extensive experience investing in and managing financial institutions.
            





Strategy

        	Lightyear is deeply embedded in financial services, having invested in the industry for over 15 years through multiple market cycles and environments.  We believe our expertise in financial services and its sub-sectors allows Lightyear to quickly identify opportunities and offer resources beyond capital to portfolio companies.

            
Industry ExpertiseFinancial services is a large and complex industry, representing approximately 15% of the S&P 500.  We use top-down analysis, theme-based research, and our well-established network to drive our sourcing.  We view the industry as composed of six sectors and target growth sub-sectors within these six.  Within each fund, we strive to create a diversified portfolio.
             


Asset Management
Financial Technology
Banks
Insurance
Brokerage
Specialty Finance




Creating Value
          We believe our extensive experience in the financial services industry helps create value for our portfolio companies and our investors.  We strive to work hand-in-hand with management teams and owners to unlock value and create stronger companies.  Below are some of the benefits and value drivers Lightyear aims to offer to our portfolio companies.
          

Access to Lightyear Network
Transaction Structuring
Add-on Acquisition Support
Experience in Regulated Environments
Operational Improvements
Data Analytics and Reporting Enhancements
Strengthened Governance






