Lightyear Capital - Lightyear Capital Inc.











































 








































 
 









 

























 




 



Lightyear Capital
















Who We Are
Lightyear Capital Inc. is a private, independent investment dealer servicing Canadian corporate clients and institutional investors through investment banking and sales and trading services. In addition, Lightyear offers financial services to high-net-worth clients as a strategic private wealth and asset management advisor.




