Regulatory Disclosures


Lightyear Capital Inc. > Regulatory Disclosures















Lightyear Capital Inc. is member of the Investment Industry Regulatory Organization of Canada (“IIROC”), the TMX Group and the Canadian Investor Protection Fund (“CIPF”). Lightyear is registered in Alberta, Ontario, British Columbia, Saskatchewan and Manitoba and services client accounts in the jurisdictions in which it is registered.
